data.description: Mayfield     This home offers 3 Bedrooms, and 2.5 Bathrooms with a Loft. The great room opens to the kitchen with a large center island with bar stool seating. There is a Mud Room off the garage entry with optional valet or cubbies.  Dining area off kitchen with large rear patio/deck.  Upstairs has a primary suite, loft, 2 bedrooms, laundry room, and hall bath. The home is currently under construction. Please contact the listing agent for more details on the home.
